description: Lists all asset bundle export jobs that have been taken place in the last 14 days. Jobs created more than 14 days ago are deleted forever and are not returned. If you are using the same job ID for multiple jobs, ListAssetBundleExportJobs only returns the most recent job that uses the repeated job ID.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that the export jobs were executed in.

nested_items.name: AssetBundleExportJobSummaryList
nested_items.description: A list of export job summaries.

nested_items.name: JobStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the export job.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the export job.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that the export job was created.

nested_items.name: AssetBundleExportJobId
nested_items.description: The ID of the export job.

nested_items.name: IncludeAllDependencies
nested_items.description: The flag that determines the inclusion of resource dependencies in the returned asset bundle.

nested_items.name: ExportFormat
nested_items.description: The format for the export job.

nested_items.name: IncludePermissions
nested_items.description: The flag that determines the inclusion of permissions associated with each resource ARN.

nested_items.name: IncludeTags
nested_items.description: The flag that determines the inclusion of tags associated with each resource ARN.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
